  A): Goa2 siuN7 se3-kan te7-it iau3-kin2 si7 chiN5, siok8-gu2 kong2 ¡§U7 chiN5 sai2 kui2 e7 e-bou7¡¨, a2-si7 kong2 ¡§ChiN5 na7 bo5, lang5 chiu7 so5¡¨. ChhiaN2 li2 siuN7 khah chin, bo5 lun7 beh cho3 sim2-mih8, kiam2 u7 chit8-hang7 m7-bian2 chiN5 e7 eng7 tit e5, bo5 chiN5 chiu7 kiaN5 bo5 lou7, kim-chiN5 si7 ban7-leng5. sou2-i2 goa2 toa7-han3 e5 si5, beh piaN3-se3 than3 chiN5, thang chiaN5 cho3 toa7 pu3-ong. 
  B): Goa2 siuN7 se3-kan te7 it iau3-kin2 tioh8 u7 hak8-bun7, siok8-Gu2 kong2 ¡§Chit8 ji7 tat8 chhian-kim¡¨, u7 chiN5 chin che7, na7 m7 bat ji7, ma7 si7 chheN-me5 gu5, ¡§Jin5 put hak8, put ti gi7¡¨, lang5 na7 m7-bat ji7, sia2 phoe ia7 chin put pian7. Sou2-i2 goa2 beh piaN3 se3 thak8 chheh, au7-lai5 cho3 phok-su7, cho3 gau5-lang5 ......... 
  C): Goa2 siuN7 sin-the2 kian7-khong iong2-kiaN7 te7 it iau3-kin2, u7 chiN5 u7 hak8-bun7, na7 lam2-sin-mia7, tak8-jit8 teh chiah8 ioh8, thai2 u7 sim2-mih8 heng7-hok? Sou2-i2 goa2 beh kou3 goa2 e5 seng-khu hou7 i iong2-kiaN7, thang chiah8 kau3 lau7 khok-khok. 
  D): Goa2 siuN7 se3-kan thit-tho5 siang7 iau3-kin2, kou2-cha2 lang5 kong2 ¡§Jin5-seng jiok8 bong7, ui7-hoan ki ho5?¡¨ i3-su3 chiu7 si7, jin5-seng na2 chhin-chhiuN7 chit8 tiuN5 e5 bin5-bang7, hoaN-hi2 e5 si5 bo5 kui2 pai2, sou2-i2 goa2 beh piaN3-se3 lai5 thit-tho5, in-ui7 chit8 si3 lang5 bo5 loa7 ku2. 
  E): Goa2 siuN7 se3-kan te7-it iau3-kin2 tioh8 lau5 mia5-siaN, siok8-gu2 kong2: ¡§Hou2 si2 lau5 phe5, lang5 si2 lau5 mia5¡¨, u7 chiN5, u7 hak8-bun7, u7 iong2-kiaN7 e5 seng-khu, thang tak8-jit8 thit-tho5, si2 liau2 au7, na7 phaiN2 mia5-siaN, si7 chin bo5 ke3-tat8. Sou2-i2 goa2 beh chhut-lat8 siu-iong2, lau5 mia5-siaN kau3 au7 se3-tai7. 
  F): Goa2 siuN7 se3-kan pak-tou2 e7 pa2 siang7 te7 it iau3-kin2, mia5-siaN bo5 lou7 eng7, siok8-gu2 kong2: ¡§Chiah8 loh8 pak, un2-tak-tak¡¨, tak8 jit8 na7 u7 hi5, u7 bah, hou7 goa2 thang chiah8 kau3 pa2, goa2 chiu7 chin boan2-chiok, na7 beh si2 lah, ma7 beh chiah8 hou7 i chit8 tou7 pa2-pa2 thang cho3 pa2 kui2. 
  G): Chu-ui7, goa2 khoaN3 lin2 chiah e5 long2 si7 hian7-se3 chu2-gi7, but8-chit chu2-gi7 kap hiong2-lok8 chu2-gi7, long2 bo5 teh siuN7 au7-lai5 e5 tai7-chi3 ...... goa2 siuN7 se3-kan te7 it iau3-kin2 tioh8 sin3 Ia5-sou chiah u7 eng2-oan2 e5 hok-khi3, u7 chiN5, u7 hak8-bun7, iong2-kiaN7, ho2 mia5-siaN, tak8 jit8 thang chiah8 hi5, chiah8 bah, si2 liau2-au7 leng5-hun5 ha7 loh8 te7-gek8, u7 sim2-mih8 li7-ek? 
  Kin-a2-jit8 si7 kiu3-chu2-tan3, goa2 khou2-khng3 lin2 tak8 lang5 tioh8 lai5 sin3 Ia5-sou. In-ui7 chai7-seN sin3 Ki-tok, si2-au7, chiah oe7 thang kau3 thian-kok. 
