  Ia5-sou e5 chit-giap8 
  A: Kin7-lai5 Ki-tok-kau3 chin chhiong-seng7, tak8 sou2 chai7 to u7 kau3-hoe7, siong5-siong5 thiaN-kiN3 teh pou3-to7, chong2-si7 tau3-ti2 Ia5-sou e5 chit-giap8 m7-chai si7 sim2-mih8? Kai3 tu2-ho2 Bok8-seng hiaN ti7 hia teh lai5, lai5 ka7 i mng7 khoaN3 mai7. 
  Bok8-seng hiaN, kai3 tu2-ho2, goa2 beh chheng2-kau3 li2. 
  B: Khi2-kam2, sim2-mih8 tai7-chi3? 
  A: M7-chai Ia5-sou e5 chit-giap8 si7 sim2-mih8 hoN3? 
  B: Ah, soah m7-chai si7 bak8-kang sai-hu7, I e5 iuN2-pe7 Iok-sek Si7 Na2-sat-lek8 siaN5 chhut mia5 e5 bak8-kang, sou2-i2, soah to7 koh siuN7? 
  A: Goa2 ioh I si7 kou3 iuN5 e5, in-ui7 I bat kong2, goa2 si7 ho2 e5 bok8-chia2, goa2 beh ui7 iuN5 pang3-sak seN3-mia7. 
  B: Goa2 ioh e5 khah tioh8, li2 ioh e5 m7-tioh8 lah, m7-sin3 Iu2-seng5 hiaN ti7 hia teh lai5, lai5 ka7 i chheng2-kau3. Iu2-seng5 hiaN, tau3-ti2 Ia5-sou e5 chit-giap8 si7 sim2-mih8? 
