  A: Goa2 ioh si7 bok8-chia2. 
  B: Goa2 ioh si7 bak8-kang. 
  C: Lin2 ioh e5 khah m7-tioh8, goa2 ioh e5 chiah tioh8, m7-sin3 PiaN2-sin hiaN ti7 hia teh lai5, lan2 lai5 mng7 i khoaN3 mai7. PiaN2-sin hiaN, goan2 tai7-ke teh ioh, khoaN3 Ia5-sou e5 chit-giap8 si7 sim2-mih8, chit8 lang5 ioh chit8 khoan2, taN ai3 chheng2-kau3 li2, m7-chai li2 ioh si7 sim2-mih8? 
  D: Ia5-sou si7 teh cho3-piaN2, lin2 kiam2 m7 bat thiaN tioh8 Ia5-sou ti7 khong3-ia2 iong7 piaN2 hou7 5000 lang5 chiah8 kau3 pa2, koh chhun 12 kheng, na7 m7-si7 teh cho3-piaN2 thai2 u7 thang hou7 hiah che7 lang5 chiah8, koh chhun hiah che7. 
  A: U7-iaN2 to tioh8, chong2-si7 goa2 bat khoaN3 tioh8 ang-a2 tou5 oe7 Ia5-sou pho7 iuN5-a2, khah kong2 ia7 si7 bok8-chia2 khah tioh8. 
  B: Goa2 ioh bak8-kang, Iu2-seng5 hiaN ioh si7 i-seng. 
  D: Lin2 ioh e5 long2 m7-tioh8 lah, goa2 e5 chiah tioh8 lah. 
  C: Hai2-eng2 hiaN ti7 hia teh lai5 lah, lan2 lai5 mng7 i khoaN3-mai7? 
