  S: HoN3! An2-ni kai3 ho2, tioh8 siong5-siong5 an2-ni gian2-kiu3 chiah e7 chin3-pou7. TaN lin2 sou2 ioh e5 si7 sim2-mih8? 
  A: Goa2 ioh si7 bok8-chia2. 
  B: Goa2 ioh si7 bak8-kang. 
  C: Goa2 ioh si7 i-seng. 
  D: Goa2 ioh si7 teh cho3-piaN2. 
  E: Goa2 ioh si7 tho2-hai2 lang5. 
  S: An2-ni lin2 sou2 ioh e5 long2 bo5 m7-tioh8. In-ui7 Ia5-sou si7 ho2 e5 bok8-chia2, teh chiau3-kou3 lan2, chhin-chhiuN7 bok8-chia2 chiau3-kou3 iuN5-a2; ia7 si7 gau5 ka7 lan2 siu-cheng2 lan2 phaiN2-khoaN3 e5 phin2-heng7, chiaN5-cho3 kek8 ho2 khoaN3 e5 bak8-kang; ia7 si7 gau5 i lan2 leng5-hun5 e5 peN7-cheng3 e5 toa7 i-seng; ia7-si7 chiong oah8-mia7 e5 piaN, beh hou7 lan2--e5; ia7 si7 chhin-chhiuN7 tho2-hai2 lang5 gau5 liah8 hi5. I chin gau5 chio hak8-seng. Chong2-kong2 I siang7 kin-pun2 e5 chit-giap8 chiu7-si7 beh kiu3 lang5, iau2-ku2 si7 tui3 che7-che7 hong-bin7 e5 piau2-hian7, lin2 chiah e7 ioh hiah che7 khoan2 lah.
  A: An2-ni goa2 toa7-han3 beh cho3 bok8-su, lai5 u7 hun7 ti7 Ia5-sou e5 kiu3-lang5, lai5 chiau3-kou3 Siong7-te3 e5 iuN5-kun5. 
  B: Goa2 toa7-han3 beh cho3 bak8-kang, lai5 khi2 le2-pai3 tng5. 
  C: Goa2 toa7-han3 beh cho3 i-seng, lin2 na7 pak-tou2 thiaN3, thau5-khak hin5, chhau3 kha phiN7-liam5 long2 lai5 chhoe7 goa2, bian2 chiN5 beh ka7 lin2 hong7-su7, kiam2-chio2 lang5-lang5 e5 kan-khou2. 
  E: Goa2 toa7-han3 beh liah8-hi5, ia7 beh ui7 Chu2 lai5 thoan5 to7-li2. 
  D: Goa2 beh khui piaN2-tiam3, lai5 hou7 iau e5 lang5 thang tit-tioh8 pa2. 
  S: An2-ni chin-ho2, e7-hng tu2-ho2 si7 Chu2 e5 seN-jit8, ia7 si7 lin2 e5 koat-sim e5 jit8, lin2 tioh8 siong5-siong5 e7 ki3-tit. ChhiaN2 lai5 gim5 chit8 siu2 si lai5 o-lo2 Chu2. 
